Package: ggrasp
Type: Package
Title: Gaussian-based Genome Repersentative Selector with Prioritization
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Clarke", email = "tclarke@jcvi.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Given a group of genomes and their relationship with each other, GGRaSP clusters the genomes and selects the most representitive members of each cluster. Additional data can be provided to the prioritize certain genomes. The results can be printed out as a list or a new phylogeny with graphs of the trees and distance distributions also available.
Depends: R(>= 3.1.0)
Imports: ggplot2, mixtools, ape, bgmm, colorspace, methods
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
